For example map,<br />
WP subdomain1.main.com &#8211;&gt; <a href="http://www.newsite.com/page1" rel="nofollow">http://www.newsite.com/page1</a><br />
WP subdomain2.main.com &#8211;&gt; <a href="http://www.newsite.com/page2" rel="nofollow">http://www.newsite.com/page2</a><br />
